entries.femaleVariant: So whass good? Got any plans this weekend?
Nah, just chillin' at home. Gettin' some new anti-burglary shutters put in.
No shit. How much they set you back? Was thinkin' of gettin' some myself.
More than you'd think. But if I was countin' every enny, I'd end up like my next-door neighbor. Chowin' down worms.
